**Overview**

This dashboard shows an overview of detailed information about the process, memory, file, scheduled job and kernel related activity.

Please visit the [System Activity](https://schema.ocsf.io/1.0.0/categories/system) documentation for more information.

[**Integration Page**](/app/integrations/detail/amazon_security_lake/overview)
